聆听 Oasis 罕见的另类版本“悲伤之歌”，由 Liam Gallagher 演唱https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-oasis-rare-alternative-version-of-sad-song-sung-by-liam-gallagher-3783510?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-利亚姆·加拉格尔演唱的悲伤歌曲的绿洲罕见替代版本Tom SkinnerWed, 14 Aug 2024 08:00:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3783510 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它将出现在即将发行的《Definitely Maybe》30 周年纪念再版中</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-oasis-rare-alternative-version-of-sad-song-sung-by-liam-gallagher-3783510">由 Liam Gallagher 演唱的《Listen to Oasis》罕见的另类版本“Sad Song”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>分享了由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>(Liam Gallagher) 演唱的《悲伤之歌》的罕见替代版本 - 请听下面的内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）：“世界是一个美丽的地方——只是居住着混蛋”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首原创歌曲由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)</a>演唱，是英国流行乐队 1994 年首张录音室专辑《Definitely Maybe》中的附赠曲目。</p><p>今天（8 月 14 日）他们发布了“悲伤之歌（莫尔德斯路西演示版，92 年 11 月）”，作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">该唱片 30 周年再版</a>的最新预览，该唱片将于 8 月 30 日通过 Big Brother 发行（<a href="https://oasismusic.lnk.to/DM30" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订</a>） 。</p><p>它是继之前分享的即将推出的合集中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-oasis-unheard-up-in-the-sky-monnow-valley-version-from-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-3774996">“Up In The Sky（Monnow Valley 版本）”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-columbia-sawmills-outtake-from-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-3765199">“Columbia（Sawmills Outtake）”</a>之后的版本。</p><p> 《悲伤之歌》的新演示版附带官方歌词视频 - 请在此处收听： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Oasis - Sad Song（莫尔德斯路西演示，92 年 11 月）[官方歌词视频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S1xm-P6Rpk8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Definitely Maybe》的 30 周年纪念再版有多种格式可供选择，其中将包含 Monnow Valley Studios 废弃的原始录音室的录音，以及康沃尔郡 Sawmills Studios 的最终专辑录音室的片段 - 由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>和 Callum Marinho 新混音。</p><p>描述中写道：“蒙诺谷的录音和锯木厂的录音现在首次出土，为最终完成的文章的过程提供了新的、令人信服的理解。</p><p> “凭借其原始的边缘和不安的能量，《Definitely Maybe》听起来总是像是一张已经完全成型的专辑——然而，新发布的版本为歌迷提供了对这张专辑的迷人的新见解；展示了早年推动 Oasis 发展的自信以及首次亮相所需的决心。”</p><p>它补充道：“直到现在，重新审视 30 年前的档案，表明了录音过程在讲述有史以来最重要的专辑之一的艰难创作故事方面的重要性。”</p><p>今年夏天早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-liam-gallaghers-official-footage-of-kicking-off-definitely-maybe-anniversary-tour-in-sheffield-3761988">Liam 结束了他的“Definitely Maybe”30 周年英国和爱尔兰巡演</a>，在那里他将“Half The World Away”献给了他的“弟弟”Noel。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-is-still-playing-hard-to-get-at-definitely-maybe-show-3762205">他还告诉观众，诺埃尔对于绿洲重聚“仍然表现得很难接近”</a> 。</p><p> LG 将于下周继续庆祝活动，届时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-at-reading-leeds-2024-3548140#:~:text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024-,Liam%20Gallagher%20to%20play%20Oasis'%20'Definitely%20Maybe'%20in,full%20at%20Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024&amp;text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%20have%20confirmed%20that,headline%20the%20festival%20in%202024.">他将在 Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 的头条演出中完整播放这张专辑</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 于格拉斯顿伯里和纳内沃斯 (Glastonbury &amp; Knebworth) 的石玫瑰 (The Stone Roses) 演出第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j27A15yBBE8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-on-the-chances-of-a-whats-the-story-morning-glory-anniversary-tour-3764529">LG 谈到了 2025 年举行“(What&#39;s The Story) Morning Glory”30 周年纪念巡演的可能性</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-he-is-still-trying-to-live-up-to-the-success-of-oasis-definitely-maybe-and-whats-the-story-morning-glory-3782728">Noel Gallagher 表示他仍在努力“不辜负”Oasis 前两张专辑的成功</a>。</p><p> “我们从‘Definitely Maybe’巡演的最后一晚直接开始录制‘(What&#39;s The Story) Morning Glory?’，然后花了接下来的 29 年——而且还在继续——努力不辜负两张专辑的期望，”他回忆道。</p><p> “我们知道这些歌曲很棒，因为我们每天晚上都会播放它们，而且所有的表演都令人震惊。但在当时，这只是一张好专辑——仅此而已。只是随着时间的推移，才变成了现在这个样子。”</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-responds-to-fan-in-crowd-who-asks-about-oasis-reunion-3781805">最近也在 Y Not Festival 上回应了一位粉丝，</a>当时他们询问他在他的头条新闻中是否有可能与 Oasis 重聚。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-oasis-rare-alternative-version-of-sad-song-sung-by-liam-gallagher-3783510">由 Liam Gallagher 演唱的《Listen to Oasis》罕见的另类版本“Sad Song”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
