MI》、《Anarchy In The UK》等热门歌曲。</p><p>您可以观看该节目的粉丝镜头并查看下面的社交媒体反应。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="性手枪壮举。弗兰克·卡特“尸体”在伦敦布什厅现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oTNQNwLD5M0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sex Pistols &amp; Frank Carter - Liar (现场@布什厅，伦敦)" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gs5VKxYziQ4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sex Pistols ft Frank Carter “EMI” 于 2024 年 8 月 13 日在伦敦布什大厅现场直播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0RSFi2tU2dU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">这只是性手枪（与弗兰克卡特） <a href="https://t.co/kZkibu8w81">pic.twitter.com/kZkibu8w81</a></p><p> — 尼尔·麦考密克 (@neil_mccormick) <a href="https://twitter.com/neil_mccormick/status/1823455430917398865?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 13 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">弗兰克卡特的性手枪今晚太棒了！</p><p>曾经在 Gallows 演出中看过 Frank 翻唱 Pistol 歌曲<br />很高兴见到他现在在乐队面前参加这些特别表演<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f64c.png" alt="🙌" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/1